sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User (Browser)
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS (edge)
    participant UI as Streamlit UI<br/>8501/TCP HTTP
    participant API as Backend API<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Ollama as Ollama LLM<br/>11434/TCP HTTP
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP Password
    participant LLMOpt as llm-optimizer<br/>(in-process)
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MCat as Model Catalog<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,MCat: Flow 1: Recommendation Pipeline

    User->>Route: HTTPS request
    Route->>UI: HTTP/8501 (TLS terminated)
    UI->>API: POST /api/v1/extract<br/>HTTP/8000 (no auth)
    API->>Ollama: POST /api/chat<br/>HTTP/11434 (no auth)
    Ollama-->>API: Structured DeploymentIntent
    API-->>UI: Extracted intent + specification

    UI->>API: POST /api/v1/ranked-recommend-from-spec<br/>HTTP/8000 (no auth)
    API->>PG: SELECT benchmarks<br/>PostgreSQL/5432 (password)
    PG-->>API: Benchmark results
    API->>LLMOpt: Roofline estimation<br/>(library call, in-process)
    LLMOpt-->>API: Performance estimates
    API-->>UI: 5 ranked recommendation views

    UI->>API: POST /api/v1/deploy<br/>HTTP/8000 (no auth)
    API-->>UI: Generated YAML contents<br/>(KServe, HPA, ServiceMonitor)

    Note over User,MCat: Flow 2: Deployment to Cluster

    UI->>API: POST /api/v1/deploy-to-cluster<br/>HTTP/8000 (no auth)
    API->>K8s: kubectl apply<br/>HTTPS/6443 (SA token, TLS 1.2+)
    K8s-->>API: Deployment created
    API-->>UI: Deployment status

    UI->>API: GET /api/v1/deployments/{id}/k8s-status<br/>HTTP/8000
    API->>K8s: kubectl get<br/>HTTPS/6443 (SA token)
    K8s-->>API: InferenceService status
    API-->>UI: K8s deployment status

    Note over User,MCat: Flow 3: Model Catalog Sync (background)

    API->>MCat: GET /api/model_catalog/v1alpha1<br/>HTTPS/8443 (Bearer token, service CA)
    MCat-->>API: Benchmark data + model artifacts
    API->>PG: INSERT benchmarks<br/>PostgreSQL/5432 (password)

    Note over User,MCat: Flow 4: Capacity Planning

    UI->>API: POST /api/v1/model-info<br/>HTTP/8000 (no auth)
    API->>HF: GET model metadata<br/>HTTPS/443 (Bearer HF_TOKEN, optional)
    HF-->>API: Model config + safetensors info
    API-->>UI: Model metadata

    UI->>API: POST /api/v1/calculate<br/>HTTP/8000 (no auth)
    API-->>UI: GPU memory estimates<br/>(weights, KV cache, activation)
